         <abstract>
            <p>The condition number of the Gram matrix associated with piecewise polynomial finite element bases is discussed in general, and computed explicitly for cubic splines and cubic Hermite polynomials. In the latter case, we discuss the inherent ambiguity in the basis, and find the minimum condition number.</p>
          </abstract>
